;186(3):648-56.\nPMID: 20298479<\/p>\n","answer_id":1148,"question_id":1101,"up_vote_count":1}],"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/questions/1101/how-would-a-plant-sprout-and-grow-in-a-zero-gravity-environment","last_activity_date":1329927031,"creation_date":1329749342,"answer_count":2,"title":"How would a plant sprout and grow in a zero gravity environment?","body":"<p>Have any experiments been carried out involving sprouting and growing plants in a zero gravity environment? If so, what was the outcome? How did the plants sprout out of the soil without gravity? Did they grow outward or toward light sources?<\/p>\n","question_id":1101,"tags":["plant-physiology"],"score":5,"accepted_answer_id":1102,"down_vote_count":0,"is_answered":true,"view_count":1978,"up_vote_count":5},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://i.stack.imgur.com/XDA2o.jpg?s=128&g=1","user_type":"registered","user_id":338,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/338/j-musser","reputation":1309,"display_name":"J. Musser","accept_rate":98},"answers":[{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/3cfeec7dfb47b3d98c5edf17295e959b?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":81,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/81/poshpaws","reputation":4731,"display_name":"Poshpaws","accept_rate":71},"score":6,"is_accepted":true,"comments":[{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/889548c1e8387b3d381853dee5212cfd?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":3632,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/3632/shigeta","reputation":22684,"display_name":"shigeta","accept_rate":86},"score":0,"post_id":1143,"edited":false,"creation_date":1329905013,"comment_id":1357,"body":"just to add my link.  This guy has patiently grafted 11 fruit to a single tree.  <a href=\"http://inventorspot.com/articles/lemon_tree_japan_bears_eleven_ki_9572\" rel=\"nofollow\">inventorspot.com/articles/lemon_tree_japan_bears_eleven_ki_9572<\/a>"},{"owner":{"profile_ima